
## GET token en fournissant :
curl -X POST http://localhost:8764/oauth2/token -d "grant_type=client_credentials&scope=read write" -u client1:secret1 -H "Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded"

## Test /hello endpoint:
curl -X GET http://localhost:8764/api/hello -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_GENERATED_TOKEN"

